Popular Nigerian singer, Teni goes against Cheating and stingy boyfriend in her performance in Portugal. Teni was seen teaching her fans a new song against cheating and stingy boyfriends as the ladies were seen shouting and screaming the song at the top of their voices. Teni is in Portugal for Afro Nation festival as she wows fans with her act. She said: “Bye bye to cheater, cheater, Bye bye to useless boyfriend, bye bye to stingy boyfriend, In the name of Jesus bye bye to useless boyfriend” See Photos: Watch the video below: Source